Package: fightr
Type: Package
Title: Analyze Fight Probabilities and Props via Statistical Frameworks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Benjamin", "Smith",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Predicts the probability of a win and method of victory for a 
    matchup between two fighters. Features multiple statistical frameworks 
    including multinomial logistic regression, Bradley-Terry, and 
    Thurstone-Mosteller network models.
